### Patents
Caffeinate Labs Inc. is a US-based company specializing in the design, manufacture, and distribution of consumer products as well as software for improved business workflows. Caffeinate Labs' technology can be found in our retail products and in certain products offered by our commercial partners.

This page is intended to serve as notice under 35 U.S.C. § 287(a).
